# 📚 Readers Book Bank - ASP.NET Core MVC Application

## 📖 Project Overview

Readers Book Bank is a multi-layer ASP.NET Core MVC web application developed for managing books and their availability status.

The application allows admins to:

- ➕ Add new books
- 📋 View all books
- ✏️ Edit existing books
- ❌ Delete books
- ✅ Track availability status

This project follows a layered architecture using:

- ASP.NET Core MVC
- Entity Framework Core
- SQL Server
- Repository Pattern
- Scaffolding
- Bootstrap UI

---

# 🚀 Technologies Used

- ASP.NET Core MVC (.NET 8)
- Entity Framework Core
- SQL Server
- Bootstrap
- Razor Views
- C#
- Visual Studio

---

